reda Hicks  Principal  Perry Harrison Elementary School Freda Hicks is currently the principal of Perry Harrison Elementary School in Pittsboro  NC  Perry Harrison was recently named a top three STEM elementary school by FETC in Orlando Florida  She has lead Perry Harrison s transformation to a STEM focused school the past three years   Kimberly Boyer  Teacher Perry Harrison Elementary School   Elizabeth Sturdivant  Teacher  Perry Harrison Elementary School Creating a Culture of STEM in Elementary School   Grades 3 6  Administrators Perry Harrison School will share their story of creating a STEM culture in an elementary school  We will share how building a STEM team and incorporating community goals into a successful STEM program  We will share integrating other academic areas into your STEM program  This workshop covers project based learning for teaches and administrators with students in grades 3 6  Instructors   Freda Hicks  Principal  Perry Harrison Elementary School Freda Hicks is currently the principal of Perry Harrison Elementary School in Pittsboro  NC  Perry Harrison was recently named a top three STEM elementary school by FETC in Orlando Florida  She has lead Perry Harrison s transformation to a STEM focused school the past three years   Kimberly Boyer  Teacher Perry Harrison Elementary School   Elizabeth Sturdivant  Teacher  Perry Harrison Elementary School Perry Harrison School will share their story of creating a STEM culture in an elementary school  We will share how building a STEM team and incorporating community goals into a successful STEM program  We will share integrating other academic areas into your STEM program This workshop covers project based learning for teaches and administrators with students in grades 3 6  Instructors Freda Hicks  Principal  Perry Harrison Elementary School  Freda Hicks is currently the principal of Perry Harrison Elementary School in Pittsboro  NC  Perry Harrison was recently named a top three STEM elementary school