a is also a consultant  a national presenter  and an international Keynoter   Barbara Huneycutt  2nd Grade Teacher  Albemarle County Public Schools Girl s Geek Day  What s THAT    Grades 3 8  Administrators This workshop will cover the basics of starting up a Girl s Geek Day  which can be adapted to just about any audience  We will also share our experiences and ideas for sessions and the organization we use to work with students new to us each time we hold one  Participants will problem solve as they utilize some of our technology tools  brainstorm and use engineering design principles as they work with some of our STEM equipment  and share and collaborate as we work together to craft an entertaining  yet informative 50 minutes  This workshop covers integrated STEM for teachers and administrators of students in grades 3 8  Instructors     Paula White  Gifted Resources Teacher  Albemarle County Public Schools Paula is a learner first  teacher second  Wait grandma  reader  camper  and lots of other titles come in there  too  However  one thing is for sure you ll enjoy hearing the stories and expertise she and her co presenters have to share from their many varied experiences  Paula has taught full time in five  5  different elementary schools in Albemarle  taught every grade from K 5 and worked with and learned from a multitude of excellent educators from all over the US  Paula is also a consultant  a national presenter  and an international Keynoter   Barbara Huneycutt  2nd Grade Teacher  Albemarle County Public Schools This workshop covers integrated STEM for teachers and administrators of students in grades 3 8 Instructors Paula White  Gifted Resources Teacher  Albemarle County Public Schools Paula is a learner first  teacher second  Wait grandma  reader  camper  and lots of other titles come in there  too  However  one thing is for sure you ll enjoy hearing the stories and expertise she and her co presenters have to share from their many varied experiences  Paula